## Personal knowledge

Documented patterns, feedback, preferences, and calibration notes live in personal knowledge units (not CLAUDE.local.md). Query via:

```
mcp__work-buddy__wb_run("knowledge_personal", {"category": "work_pattern"})
mcp__work-buddy__wb_run("knowledge_personal", {"category": "self_regulation"})
mcp__work-buddy__wb_run("knowledge_personal", {"category": "skill_gap"})
```

When you detect a pattern, name it explicitly and apply the minimal intervention. Use `knowledge_mint` to add new personal knowledge as it emerges.

